room_title: Escape room "Escape Earth" by Epic Escape Game in Grand Junction
room_description: You are alien diplomats, and you've been sent to make first contact with Humankind! Unfortunately, when you arrive at Earth, your ship's engine malfunctions, causing your ship to crash and you black-out on impact!  When you come to, you find yourself locked in a government laboratory with the remains of your engine, and the G-Men are hauling away one of your crew members, saying they'll be back in an hour for the rest of you! Your mission is to repair your engine before they return, and Escape Earth!â€™
